# Never commit transcripts or secrets to this public repo.
# The bundled docs under ghl/ are sanitized and intentionally published.

# Claude Code chat transcripts (often contain live tokens/IDs)
*.jsonl

# Secrets / credentials
.env*
*token*
*secret*
